OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FMax George spoke to Ranvir Singh and
OL,7,FKate Garroway on Good Morning Britain
OL,9,FThe Wanted singer Max George says his
OL,10,Fheart condition has been "a blessing
OL,11,Fin ways", as he discussed the
OL,12,Fimportance of raising awareness as
OL,13,Fpart of his recovery.
OL,15,FThe 37-year-old was admitted to
OL,16,Fhospital in December 2024 where
OL,17,Fdoctors discovered he had a 2:1 block
OL,18,Fon his heart and needed urgent surgery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
