OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FMax, who is from Manchester, was
OL,7,Ffitted with a pacemaker that week,
OL,8,Fwhich he described as a "shock", and
OL,9,Fhas since been on the mend ` having
OL,10,Freturned to performing with duo The
OL,11,FWanted 2.0 last year.
OL,13,FHe is now backing a new campaign by
OL,14,Fthe British Heart Foundation (BHF) to
OL,15,Fraise awareness of people living with
OL,16,Fheart conditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
