PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FThe singer started publicly speaking
OL,7,Fabout his heart problems during his
OL,8,Ftime in hospital almost two years ago,
OL,9,Fwhen he documented the experience on
OL,10,FInstagram due to "boredom".
OL,12,FHe said: "To interact with people was
OL,13,Fjust something nice to do. But the
OL,14,Fmore I spoke to people, the more I
OL,15,Frealised that there was a lot of
OL,16,Fpeople my age and younger that have
OL,17,Fhad this happen to them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FIt kind of triggered a thought process
OL,7,Fthat it was important to get the word
OL,8,Fout there ` that (heart problems)
OL,9,Fdon't just happen to people over 75."
OL,11,F"If I can help them with their story
OL,12,For help bring more money towards
OL,13,Ftreatment for heart conditions, then
OL,14,FI'm all for it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
