PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FHe added: "In terms of that, this
OL,7,Fwhole thing has been a blessing in
OL,8,Fways, because it's been really
OL,9,Frewarding speaking to people,
OL,10,Fespecially people that are younger
OL,11,Fthan me, and helping them feel a
OL,12,Flittle bit better about their case."
OL,14,FGeorge was diagnosed a heart block
OL,15,Fwhich, according to the NHS website,
OL,16,Fis caused by a problem with the
OL,17,Felectrical pulses controlling the
OL,18,Fheartbeat and can be helped by having
OL,19,Fa pacemaker fitted to keep the heart
OL,20,Fbeating regularly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
