PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FHe said: "It was mad. I knew something
OL,7,Fwas seriously wrong, because I could
OL,8,Fhardly breathe, and my arms and my
OL,9,Fchest were blue ` and my face. It was
OL,10,Fa shock more than anything.
OL,12,F"My heart rate was so low at that
OL,13,Ftime, it was at around 24 (beats per
OL,14,Fminute) and it was like that for about
OL,15,Feight days whilst I was in hospital
OL,16,Fwaiting for the operation."
OL,18,FAs part of the BHF campaign, Max will
OL,19,Fspeak with people who have heart
OL,20,Fconditions and they will swap stories
OL,21,Fabout their experiences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
