OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772190104
OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FHe says he is "genuinely buzzing" to
OL,7,Ftake part in the launch that will see
OL,8,Fthe charity unveil 65 red benches `
OL,9,Fone for each year it has been
OL,10,Festablished ` across the UK in tribute
OL,11,Fto those living with cardiovascular
OL,12,Fdisease.
OL,14,FEach bench carries the name of a
OL,15,Fsurvivor - plus a short message about
OL,16,Fthem and what they enjoy.
OL,18,FMax said: "It feels really cool to be
OL,19,Fa part of it. This is an awesome
OL,20,Fcampaign to be supporting, and we'll
OL,21,Fjust see where it goes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
