OL,3,CMax George says heart condition has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a blessing in ways'
OL,6,FHe rose to fame in the 2010s with The
OL,7,FWanted alongside bandmates Siva
OL,8,FKaneswaran, Jay McGuiness, Nathan
OL,9,FSykes and Tom Parker ` who died in
OL,10,F2022 at the age of 33 after being
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with an inoperable brain
OL,12,Ftumour.
OL,14,FThe group, best known for songs
OL,15,Fincluding All Time Low, Glad You Came
OL,16,Fand Chasing The Sun, had two UK number
OL,17,Fone singles and four UK top 10 albums.
OL,19,FListen to the ITV News entertainment
OL,20,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
